text: Please be more careful on the termination Clause before signing up. They will not bring up the termination Clause and also my fault of not asking. I was told to pay $15,000 if I want to terminate my account on my restaurant.
Do not sign a contract with them as they have auto renew and if you decide to terminate example move to another house, $300 termination fee no exception even if its for a day or month.
Located at Seraya Rise and travelling time about 10 mintues after the Jurong Island Checkpoint.
